Title: Adds Doodletown Brook to the definition of inland waterways eligible for the local waterfront revitalization program
Summary: Adds Doodletown Brook to the definition of inland waterways eligible for the local waterfront revitalization program.
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the executive law, in relation to including Doodletown Brook in the list of inland waterways eligible for the local waterfront revitalization program
